SUMMARY:PLAY! by More than Music
LOCATION:Esplanade Recital Studio, Singapore
DESCRIPTION:More Than Music welcomes back guitarist Kevin Loh for a musical reunion with Jun Hong, Pei-Sian and Abigail. The concert places the guitar centrestage, showcasing the virtuosity and versatility of the instrument in combinations with violin, cello and piano.\n\nPerformers:\nKevin Loh, guitar\nLoh Jun Hong, violin\nNg Pei Sian, cello\nAbigail Sin, piano\n\nProgramme:\nFritz Kreisler: 3 Viennese Dances for violin and guitar\nSérgio Assad: Menino for cello and guitar\nKacper Madejek: Shred for cello and guitar\nMáximo Diego Pujol: Dos Aires for violin and guitar\nMario Castelnuovo-Tedesco: Fantasia for guitar and piano\nDmitri Shostakovich: 5 pieces, arr. violin, cello and guitar
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
